OL,3,CEmergency prison overcrowding measures
OL,4,Cactivated as more rioters sentenced
OL,6,FThe government has triggered a plan to
OL,7,Fease overcrowding in prisons, as more
OL,8,Frioters are being sentenced for their
OL,9,Frole in the recent violent disorder
OL,10,Funrest.
OL,12,FThe activation of Operation Early Dawn
OL,13,Fis set to help manage short-term
OL,14,Fprison capacity pressure in some areas
OL,15,F- including the North West.
OL,17,FIt was last used by the Conservative
OL,18,Fgovernment in May this year.
