OL,3,CEmergency prison overcrowding measures
OL,4,Cactivated as more rioters sentenced
OL,6,FThe temporary measure comes after
OL,7,Frecent weeks saw hundreds of people
OL,8,Fimprisoned in the north of England
OL,9,Ffollowing the far-right riots, in the
OL,10,Fwake of the Southport stabbings.
OL,12,FUK prisons have been operating at
OL,13,Fcritical levels for the last several
OL,14,Fyears, often with under 1 per cent
OL,15,Fcapacity.
OL,17,FIt means that defendants waiting for a
OL,18,Fcourt appearance in the north of
OL,19,FEngland will be kept in police cells
OL,20,Funtil prison space is available.
