OL,3,CEmergency prison overcrowding measures
OL,4,Cactivated as more rioters sentenced
OL,6,FPrisons and probation minister Lord
OL,7,FTimpson said: "We inherited a justice
OL,8,Fsystem in crisis and exposed to shocks.
OL,10,F"As a result, we have been forced into
OL,11,Fmaking difficult but necessary
OL,12,Fdecisions to keep it operating.
OL,14,F"However, thanks to the hard work of
OL,15,Four dedicated staff and partners, we
OL,16,Fhave brought forward additional prison
OL,17,Fplaces and now introduced Operation
OL,18,FEarly Dawn to manage the pressure felt
OL,19,Fin some parts of the country."
