OL,3,CEmergency prison overcrowding measures
OL,4,Cactivated as more rioters sentenced
OL,6,FNational Police Chiefs' Council lead
OL,7,Ffor custody, deputy chief constable
OL,8,FNev Kemp, said: "We are working
OL,9,Fclosely with criminal justice system
OL,10,Fpartners to manage demand in the
OL,11,Fsystem and ensure that the public are
OL,12,Fsafe.
OL,14,F"Policing will continue to arrest
OL,15,Fanyone that they need to in order to
OL,16,Fkeep the public safe, including
OL,17,Fpolicing protests and events and
OL,18,Fensuring that people are arrested as
OL,19,Fexpected."
