OL,3,CEmergency prison overcrowding measures
OL,4,Cactivated as more rioters sentenced
OL,6,FIt comes as a 45th person has been
OL,7,Fcharged following violent disorder in
OL,8,FMerseyside.
OL,10,FViolent scenes flared in Southport on
OL,11,FJuly 30 and then in Liverpool city
OL,12,Fcentre and Walton on August 3.
